interestingcomments.content: I was born and raised in the Detroit vicinity, did my undergrad in Ann Arbor. Just got back from an unplanned trip there a week ago, sadly it was to bury my mother. Greenfield Village is very interesting, was there on numerous field trips as a school kid. Every LHSA event I've been to has been very enjoyable, expect this one will be likewise. Hope y'all have a great time.
